        "subtitle": "What is required for a VCF claim",
        "intro": "A VCF claim requires a complete set of documents across four categories. Missing or insufficient documents in any category will result in a Missing Information letter — which B&M typically receives before the client and which we must  must respond to within the timeline given in the letter.",
